{"tid":1504802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心呢個人。專影人大頭","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T11:54:51.000Z","uid":163492,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f902515e5ff7439cfdb21a3b7044a498acfebed0","tid":1504802,"uid":163492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRrNPEW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRrNPEW.png&h=275d514b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PYevNrL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPYevNrL.png&h=0745c288&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJJwwTz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJJwwTz.png&h=e3418ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遊行既時候<br />\n見住佢影人大頭<br />\n佢影既人 應該係前線手足<br />\n初頭唔敢肯定<br />\n因為普通記者都會影相<br />\n但佢俾人發現左<br />\n拿拿聲 用WeChat send左張相<br />\n就del 左  跟住俾人追問<br />\n佢話邊個app流暢就用<br />\n跟住又想跑走 <br />\n問佢邊間報管<br />\n佢話wnd <br />\n講左搵唔到間野完來<br />\n係大公報 點新聞 <br />\n<br />\n佢自己影人大頭 但係又係咁叫人 唔好影佢<br />\n同埋佢唔識英文 有口音"},{"pid":"323012a9f1bb742b898a203a202cca84d51a51af","tid":1504802,"uid":163492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"大家可以去FB睇下點新聞係咩黎"},{"pid":"1c6c7da5960c7d8ce3919a29fbc705631e3532ab","tid":1504802,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,待定, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機9月6(五)搞埋</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全部1點，唯一底線，唔衝禁區(會變恐襲)</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"c